/**
 * Causes Office to return descriptive error when the add-in wants to access MS Graph and the user/admin has not granted consent to MS Graph scopes. Office only supports consent to graph scopes when the add-in has been deployed by a tenant admin. This information will not be available during development. Setting this option to true will allow Office to inform your add-in beforehand if MS graph access will fail by returning back a descriptive error.
 */

